    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to land that verges on a lake. In extended use the term is used to describe administrative regions or landmasses on or in the vicinity of a lake, or recreational areas that include lake access.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
